{
  "id": "RAW_233f6197",
  "title": "OpenAI 把手伸进你的钱包了！ChatGPT 打通银行 API，全网炸锅：这是给黑客发年终奖？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651284432&idx=1&sn=a86f3d6f9a9f3d8ac0ff6dda35060862",
  "date": "2026-05-16 05:01:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span>作者｜冬梅 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1520a422&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNhaQJFjicbmqHdsg5jCjwaD6stAJQIsG2YlsUlWGKrETVfxfiauT5JS6MKOAY8T6JpulY8YBUvYBSr3LoSOw5UBpPD8M3PeURjicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>1</span></span><span>&nbsp;ChatGPT 可以帮你理财了，但也用你的数据训练模型 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>昨晚，OpenAI 正式面向美国地区的 ChatGPT Pro 用户推出全新个人理财体验预览版。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>该功能允许用户安全连接个人金融账户，通过专属仪表盘查看资金流向，并结合自身财务状况向 ChatGPT 提出个性化咨询，全程由用户掌控核心信息，目前仅面向小部分用户试点，后续将逐步优化扩展。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1c2cf75&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjlf9gibxuWBlcF0d72M25xnlorYXIqR290ZeBU0I5fI5rMFnCIwCPhuc1gT9NQlj2x9vLiaic5hHFibWzQonrnzU4gpyib5D8NeGqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>OpenAI 表示，与关联金融账户的对话将遵循与常规 ChatGPT 相同的模型训练设置。这意味着，除非用户选择退出，否则 OpenAI 可以将这些对话用作训练数据。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>OpenAI 表示，金钱深刻影响着人们生活的方方面面，从居住选择、家庭照料到未来规划，都与财务状况紧密相关。但当前理财场景中，用户往往需要整合多个账户、应用程序、信用卡及贷款信息，甚至借助电子表格汇总，才能勉强掌握自身财务全貌，后续的规划决策更是无从下手。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span><span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>所以新推出的个人理财功能，其核心亮点在于将 GPT-5.5 的推理能力与用户实际财务状况、个人目标、生活方式及优先级相结合，帮助用户发现财务规律、权衡决策利弊，提供更具个性化和全面性的财务规划建议。用户可通过该功能咨询各类具体财务问题，例如消费变化分析、中长期储蓄计划制定等，但 OpenAI 明确提示，该功能仅提供信息参考，不能取代专业财务建议。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>OpenAI 举了一些具体的例子：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>这款个人理财助手可以帮你规划支出，比如想在 5 年内买套房子，就可以询问它的建议了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=baf0f61b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaU6TrLpZzpYWic2qC85qicCSuKKOmic8ye7zTO3fv2NicpqCvCY11kl61xaNEdjPsVMw11yj52NSnFPScfUJic9FS6EwHpwnbjok4E%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>不知道一趟旅行到底花了多少钱？它可以给你出一份清晰的账单。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f3b606c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhWy094cy9jVnPOjPSyLSeJtPtRPAYeaFFO4Wwv4OKmGkfUXRo70MrLI3tTN1zKPa21NzWyG3gFsgyBG5VxYeIbVj2DpA2x7ibc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>再比如最近支出太多了，让它帮你看看哪里可以省下来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40ed80e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNia698mIQhpKKroFxnlYOnuRaNCKiavKNKqDQQMj9hsJpjUkzvU8kGgoB7obyB7O0fnF63IhrXCAOtoaelQepSica2gKtP25ZdP4E%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>还可以帮你在财务上设定某种假设，比如以我现在的经济状况，我能否找一份更低薪水的工作，让我有更多时间和自由陪伴孩子？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cc6aa82e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhF8EekOYEd1KarH79Dk7fOHGhAGeLdvfhJwcYHrEsGqTIN8Q8TzFpq35wDocE1Ywl4gpnYm25H4T6exyBVfypAPpQto6NYALM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>甚至连日常生活中的投资风险也会给你做出预警。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06ef00a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNiasMT2wfF2ZB8jpp3VBNGcNKKOjEaWNbfFGs5Meiat0M5IicNDnsKPGiagibWyttfz0N61cVXfYibOaUTxiaE8YZhu0ley7r2ZPGWjck%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>也能帮你审查你的哪些订阅服务是花了冤枉钱。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f14e37b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhFAVQztZg0TUqwFsvMQ4NDIZUiafHbqtnwwFkdT2XB5tVr2auxcV7YSDaqBNia2PgD3gEvvE6DMyDd8dxjlzuaW1OUu6NCBUEQE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>据统计，每月已有超过 2 亿用户通过 ChatGPT 进行预算规划、投资咨询、投资路径对比及未来财务目标规划等操作。而 GPT-5.5 模型的最新进展，进一步提升了 ChatGPT 处理个人理财领域复杂、上下文相关问题的能力，为此次新功能推出奠定了技术基础。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>据悉，该理财功能目前已在 ChatGPT 网页版和 iOS 版同步上线，仅对美国 Pro 用户开放，支持超过 12000 家金融机构的账户连接。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>OpenAI 计划根据早期用户的使用反馈持续优化体验，后续将逐步推广至 Plus 用户，最终实现所有用户均可使用的目标。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>这一功能的推出，距离 OpenAI 今年 4 月收购个人理财初创公司 Hiro 的团队仅一个月时间，Hiro 团队的金融专业知识为该功能的研发提供了支持。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43ad4b2f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNiapl41m163MOicrsJa6bOuELBK3hvMruicjmdpRUUAPhCTyeKIwK5U72SWfQ1M0q5g38ic1gaZCrCx31KwoCFRs9ykO6ibws67lTQ8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>2</span></span><span>&nbsp;与同类产品有何不同？ </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>那么，ChatGPT 的新功能与目前现有的预算平台（例如 Rocket Money 和 Monarch）有何不同？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>一句话概括起来，就是——ChatGPT 会记住用户的重要信息，并在回答问题时牢记这些信息，但不会进行任何操作。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>OpenAI 产品经理 Ty Geri 在一次简报会上表示，这些新功能将有助于“将您的个人财务状况与更广泛的个人生活状况联系起来”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb8b55c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNj1aM5DLtMXliaTR0HLNPB0qHnKhicqeWiccPZVibMyqd4Gj9EDrxEHFJLce2OKHeZiaxgNcLQa9ylFawjvSrE39tIS4LiabhWngIiatA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>Geri 说，如果你让 ChatGPT 帮你找出不需要的订阅服务，这个助手会利用它已有的关于你的信息来给出建议。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>在简报中，OpenAI 强调 ChatGPT 仅拥有读取用户财务信息的权限，它只能分析数据，而不能实际操作用户的资金，例如进行投资或取消订阅。这些操作仍然需要用户自行完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>那该怎么使用呢？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>据 OpenAI 介绍，开启这一理财体验的操作十分便捷。用户可从 ChatGPT 侧边栏打开“财务”选项并选择“开始使用”，也可在对话任意位置输入“@Finances，连接我的账户”启动流程。ChatGPT 会引导用户通过 Plaid 平台安全关联金融账户，Intuit 平台的支持将在后续推出。完成身份验证后，系统将同步并分类用户财务数据，整个过程约需几分钟。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>该公司在新闻稿中表示，ChatGPT 将能够“访问用户的余额、交易记录、投资和负债，以帮助用户更直观地了解财务状况或解答您的疑问”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>账户同步完成后，用户可通过专属仪表盘，实时查看投资组合表现、支出明细、订阅服务及即将到期的付款等核心财务信息。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>除关联账户外，用户还可主动分享房贷、储蓄目标、计划大额消费等个性化财务信息，这些内容将被保存至“财务记忆”中，为后续对话提供参考，让 ChatGPT 能够结合账户数据与用户需求，提供更具针对性的指导。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f6170f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNia52eMNeCBgHUF8QLwhVP9g6vyvXE5CXtwU8Lz9HaYXkIxRVgITC4hrZbED4prolGnzXSCP6Ecj1gROZJRg10ssic1brIhF4XQs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>为实现“从解答到行动”的理财服务闭环，OpenAI 正与 Intuit 等生态系统合作伙伴携手。依托 Intuit 的技术支持，用户可在 ChatGPT 平台内完成从信用卡推荐、审批概率查询到申请提交，从股票出售税务影响咨询、税务估算到预约当地税务专家实时咨询等一系列操作，实现财务咨询与实际行动的无缝衔接。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>针对财务数据的隐私与安全问题，OpenAI 作出明确承诺，将用户掌控权放在首位。关联账户后，ChatGPT 仅能访问用户的账户余额、交易记录、投资及负债信息，无法查看完整账号，也不能对账户进行任何操作。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>为了进一步解释其安全性，OpenAI 还表示，用户可随时通过“设置”&gt;“应用”&gt;“财务”或“财务”页面断开账户连接，断开后同步的账户数据将在 30 天内从 OpenAI 系统中删除，且不影响对话历史中的财务信息，用户也可单独删除相关对话。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>同时，用户可在“财务”页面查看或删除“财务记忆”中的内容；使用临时聊天功能时，ChatGPT 不会访问关联的金融账户，且临时聊天记录不会留存。此外，用户可启用多重身份验证（MFA），进一步提升账户安全性。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>为确保理财建议的准确性和质量，与关联金融账户相关的对话默认使用 GPT-5.5 Thinking 模型——OpenAI 最新的推理模型。OpenAI 还建立了内部评估基准，联合来自领先机构的 50 多位金融专业人士，对 ChatGPT 在复杂个人理财任务中的表现进行全面评估。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>最后，OpenAI 还强调了这项新功能背后支撑的模型是其最先进的 GPT-5.5 Thinking 模型。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>评估结果显示，GPT-5.5 Thinking 在复杂理财任务中的表现优于前代模型，其中适用于 ChatGPT Pro 用户的 GPT-5.5 Pro 模型表现最佳。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>在针对挑战性财务任务的个人理财基准测试中，GPT-5.5 Thinking 得分为 79 分（满分 100 分），GPT-5.5 Pro 得分为 82.5 分（满分 100 分），该得分是专家对回答质量和准确率的加权综合评分。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3639ef54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNiadd7zHFs5ibSBETkAjdR9D7ZhqGJsuGhhjFoIy4sLxxbpIg94Z8NwIDmnebibcpxzc2g9QNgekqicoYHXcJHZ9vedElOicvlkYHDc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e72aa4a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNiam7NYUIgclAE61dSvoPGtZp1optI9cnE0Z8H74phHfIZib9dARhANe4yeSULVMtCXgqxUBSlRIJtdflDhTMxRDIpczSGxicjUlM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>3</span></span><span>&nbsp;你会让 ChatGPT 管理你的钱包吗？ </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>ChatGPT 推出个人理财功能后，围绕“让 AI 接管钱包”这件事，互联网很快分裂成了两派。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>一派的第一反应几乎是本能的警惕。有人直言：“把银行账户权限交给 AI，这件事在我看来太疯狂了。谢谢，不必。有些数据就应该永远保持私密。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8224378&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjPgUkTZNI9tYh2wheE1AmDhMHnaw12ESxozibaWgmT0HrRibIYFUo9TWSR7M4TTTUhuv1ExfcpxVm0vOGxKxiaXk855ssGossz00%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5421e14&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjjPnkMS41Dxe3aicEibcHSdOnECeiaCohUKwnymYn1peYhwzqgECFhWwTfSnhbaDr7HpBicXlsNdJ7PPqPCtqKMQRR6OmYMVLmSQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>在他们看来，聊天记录、搜索偏好、日常习惯已经足够让平台勾勒出用户画像，而一旦金融账户被打通，AI 掌握的将不只是兴趣偏好，而是一个人最核心的资产流向、消费结构甚至风险承受能力。对不少人而言，这已经越过了技术便利的边界，进入了隐私不可退让的禁区。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0691552&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjGicBk8WIk0JqRBV3QFUhTeeDUr0bJduG3ynT8qoGI3TkmlF0pPw2Yt28mzJph1ic0SjxM5vz5DmduC5yVfPERT89NxqFkaEkjc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=075fb8bf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNhLgkJgqg4E4GNCG0Rl3qZr9Z0VCj6vqnr1a4K3XNdFT2NXoB2sTmB9uJYXJuib0cJMHsH69MM8eH3KqibEECDpGGpjr167KsPN0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>还有用户晒出了他与 ChatGPT 的对话截图，他询问 ChatGPT：即使号称“安全”，把所有的财务数据实时访问权限交给 OpenAI 是个好主意吗？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>ChatGPT 答道：“从纯粹的风险管理角度来看，任何能够持续访问你完整财务生活的系统，都不应该在绝对意义上被视为‘安全’。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb73d54f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNj0YVsx1d9icLDZ9agTxLKS0Npiadntk5rgRAphfibzmGibPaJQyzEDoV0MWNpgiaBmuq5BTUyaIaYU9Zzxu8ibmftQYpiaaplibNQGc8I%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>另一种更现实的担忧则聚焦在责任归属上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>有人评论说，个人理财 AI 技术本身并没有问题，真正的问题在于：如果某天用户醒来，发现自己的 AI 助手在一夜之间擅自开通了六项流媒体订阅服务，甚至自动完成了付款，那么责任该由谁承担？是平台算法的问题，是模型判断失误，还是用户在授权时默认接受了风险？当 AI 不再只是提供建议，而是直接连接银行账户并代替用户执行操作，现有的责任认定机制几乎无法覆盖这种新型场景。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=902292c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNia8X1VKPHKaBhBQAKc3IZ41NIVRUtnQ7Vjic3x6uzLFCg3arXICMK9p0xEy5kLA8R1RuxuZCZSGpO8HfbHtbVehia6urHgbZBZDo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>换句话说，技术已经先一步冲进现实，但规则体系还远远没有跟上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>这种担忧甚至让一些人进一步推演出了行业冲击。有人直接断言：“所有 AI 金融科技创业公司都要完蛋了。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ddb0b38&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNgOUq5KWRH9KbOkwgD90wgc2PUUkdia1f5wLheDJR9244H1KLgicvDB5QE5D175ngbOoRajDGITpNEz8vICv3w2IVq1oSgdZIsvs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>这很好理解，如果像 ChatGPT 这样的平台型产品开始切入个人理财，原本依赖“帮用户管钱”“帮用户做预算”“帮用户做消费规划”作为卖点的 AI FinTech 创业公司，护城河将被迅速稀释。毕竟在大模型时代，用户很可能更倾向于把金融权限交给一个自己已经日常使用的超级入口，而不是再额外下载一个垂直工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f2196780&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNjc8C2Vw3WBphydyrQ4s7AJaFBO5CyVHdJ67QubDsUpiatHAfP2EKiciaueZP2oPUjhJlicNc2LKic74rwLfXuoqztpRyrkKz6iaj3CU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>但支持者的声音同样强烈，而且他们给出的理由非常鲜明：年轻一代根本没有那么在意隐私。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>有人指出，许多人并没有真正理解这一代消费互联网用户的变化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>对 Z 世代乃至更年轻的用户来说，数据隐私的重要性正在让位于即时价值。只要产品确实能解决问题，他们愿意交出银行账户权限、通讯录、邮箱访问权，甚至手机相册。隐私在他们那里不是绝对原则，而是一种可以交换的资源——只要交换来的体验足够丝滑、效率足够高。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2097621&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNgm29nHx40x2ibkTBxuq4XVTUib30qmD2FDUvJr5aLATGp2u9ZhicgdbQo23zPdokACfsXD4syXMZLp1cnL5jaVDpXOVN2ibfMl9Uk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>这种态度甚至被一些年轻用户说得更直接。有人坦言：“也许是因为我骨子里就是 Z 世代，但我真的已经不在乎隐私了。我早就过了纠结隐私的阶段。我把所有财务信息、健康数据，几乎所有东西都给了 OpenAI 访问权限，我无所谓。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29b93bf5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FhLLZnAbUwNgUPICNTj3iaBXaruZk7G3gF9vscUYK3l4ygJibb4SrEAXeTq3XkAAiboS2R2gjl2DuoJb0Rzib25nRuRTJUFR4N6k0AibG4YmTxbg8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>这或许才是这场争议真正值得关注的地方。表面上看，这只是一次关于 ChatGPT 新功能的讨论；更深层次上，它折射出的其实是两种数字时代价值观的碰撞：一代人坚持“数据属于个人，绝不能轻易让渡”；另一代人则认为“隐私本质上是效率的成本，只要收益足够高，交换完全合理”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span>而当大语言模型开始从回答问题、生成内容，进一步延伸到管理用户资产、理解消费习惯、甚至替用户直接作出财务决策时，一个更尖锐的问题已经摆在所有人面前：当 AI 开始窥探你的钱包，人类究竟是在获得更聪明的助手，还是正在主动交出你的全部身家？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #888888;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://openai.com/index/personal-finance-chatgpt/\" target=\"_blank\">https://openai.com/index/personal-finance-chatgpt/</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://www.inc.com/ben-sherry/chatgpt-wants-your-bank-account-info-heres-why-you-may-actually-want-to-share-it/91345488\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inc.com/ben-sherry/chatgpt-wants-your-bank-account-info-heres-why-you-may-actually-want-to-share-it/91345488</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://x.com/ChatGPTapp/status/2055317612687675545\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/ChatGPTapp/status/2055317612687675545</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 面向美国 Pro 用户推出 ChatGPT 个人理财功能，可连接银行账户分析财务状况，但数据默认用于模型训练引发隐私争议。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 面向美国 Pro 用户推出 ChatGPT 个人理财功能，可连接银行账户分析财务状况，但数据默认用于模型训练引发隐私争议。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 OpenAI 最新推出的 ChatGPT 个人理财功能，该功能允许美国 Pro 用户通过 Plaid 平台安全连接个人金融账户，利用 GPT-5.5 Thinking 模型分析余额、交易记录、投资和负债，提供消费分析、储蓄规划、订阅审查等个性化财务建议。文章详细介绍了功能的使用方式、安全措施（只读权限、数据删除选项、MFA 支持）以及与其他理财平台（如 Rocket Money）的差异。同时，文章重点呈现了互联网上的两极反应：一方担忧隐私泄露和 AI 误操作的责任归属，认为将银行权限交给 AI 风险过高；另一方则认为年轻一代（Z 世代）更看重即时价值，愿意用隐私交换便利。文章还指出，该功能可能对 AI 金融科技创业公司形成冲击，因为用户更倾向于使用超级入口而非垂直工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
